column2: SELECT   d.ra AS input_ra, d.dec AS input_dec, s.ra as s_ra, s.dec as s_dec into mydb.MyTable_# from MyDB.CAGN_strict_radec AS d     OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq( d.ra, d.dec, #) AS n      LEFT JOIN SpecObjAll AS s ON n.objid=s.bestObjID      LEFT JOIN stellarMassStarFormingPort AS m ON m.specObjID=s.specObjID
